Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:33.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind. Open your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.80,0:00:50.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far beyond the deep blue Earth,\nyou and I shall meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.01,0:00:51.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a gentle breeze goes by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:55.38,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:56.85,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.85,0:01:03.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A snow-white feather will come\nfluttering down, swaying gently in the air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.99,0:01:11.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, I want to\nenvelope you, my one and only love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:20.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I have the power to protect\nthe one I love, right here in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:27.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind.\NJust as I've always dreamed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.25,0:01:34.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let the wind carry off\nyour hopes, faraway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:40.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have wings nobody can see.\NLook, you have them, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:49.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll take us to where we can be free.\NAnyone can be free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:53.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky is so blue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.15,0:02:07.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...so people here on Earth\nare into this kind of thing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.46,0:02:10.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you looking at, Urd?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:12.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind, it's not for kids.\N{\i1}There you go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:12.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind, it's not for kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:12.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:14.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you mean by that?\N{\i1}Thanks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:14.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:17.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, when you're\na little older, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:34.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was getting so romantic...\nIf only nothing had come between us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:37.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I need some soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:53.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:57.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you get any closer to her\nI'm going to use a Skuld bomb on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:02:59.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:03.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'd think after that day\nthey'd have made some progress...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:07.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then, I'm going to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:11.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A mandrake root, a pumpkin ghost\nstem...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:15.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The tears of a banshee,\nand a cockatrice feather...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:19.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm...it smells divine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:23.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now all I have to do is let it simmer\nfor 2 hours and get the extract.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:27.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what am I doing? Today's\nthe last episode of Winter Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:35.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! That Urd is up to no good again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:42.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cooking up a concoction like this...\nI just know she'll cause another uproar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better nip\nthis evil plan in the bud!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:50.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Darn, that show really ripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:54.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aha...all done, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:59.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Neanderthal, Cro-Magnon,\NAustralopithecus, Java...Peking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:02.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The seeds of magic,\nthe seeds of romance...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:04.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the seeds of love,\ncultivated to become strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:09.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Transform yourself into love crystals\nto forge a bond between those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:18.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Was the smoke always this\noverwhelming?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:21.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:24.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:30.53,AMG episode name red,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah! Please Don't Look at Me Like That!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:32.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}FURIN KAZAN{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:38.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good, at this rate, the shaft's\nonly going to get thicker than the gear...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:41.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, why'd he have to give\nan assignment like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:45.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, you should have something\nsweet when you're feeling tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:48.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks...huh? Urd?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:53.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When you're tired, you should have\nsomething sweet...there's nothing better!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:57.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something's fishy...I just\nknow this isn't normal candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:05:00.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, come on! Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:03.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi? I've brought you some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:05.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:08.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, what can those be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:12.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's candy...for people here on Earth.\NDo you want some, Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:15.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\N{\i1}Yes, I'd love a piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:18.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd...so it really is just candy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:22.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:24.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:29.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd? What's going on?\N{\i1}Oh, um...nothing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:31.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong...did I botch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:33.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Me of all people?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:36.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But how can that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:46.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know it didn't have to be Keiichi\nwho took those crystals, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:49.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...why isn't it taking effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:25.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:29.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Seniors...I can't go on anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is it morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:42.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I keep having these\nweird dreams lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:48.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I must be really burned out.\nI'm still dreaming...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:51.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll sleep some more...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:54.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:56.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}B...B...Belldandy!{\i0}\NGood morning, Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:57.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}B...B...Belldandy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:07:00.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me.\nI woke you up, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:05.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is Belldandy doing here?\nIn my bed, for crying out loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:08.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really my room, even?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:09.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keiichi?{\i0}\nIs this really my room, even?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:13.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but you're sweating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:16.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Were you too hot, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:22.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry! But I wanted\nto be right next to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:26.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dreaming.\NThis has got to be a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:29.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi? What's the matter, Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:30.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:33.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible! Keiichi's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:35.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:36.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:39.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those Seeds of Love pack a punch.{\i0}\NBig Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:43.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those Seeds of Love pack a punch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:47.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd, you didn't use those\nthings on Big Sister, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:50.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you seem to know a lot about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:53.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?\nI have no idea at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:59.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:05.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your temperature's normal. But\nwhat on earth's making you sweat so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:09.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, I'm fine! See?\NAll this exercise is making me sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:12.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four, five, six...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:16.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! There's nothing\nwrong with you, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:22.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:24.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, holy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:28.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let me wipe away your sweat,\nor you'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:33.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to hold still now, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:36.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a dream.\nIt's some kind of mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:40.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen Belldandy\nacting like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:45.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's your scent, Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:48.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what's\ngoing on here anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:50.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:51.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:54.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:57.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, just hurry up\nand get some clothes on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:02.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The bones of a Nauman elephant,\nthe tears of a giant sea turtle...Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:05.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm short on eternity dust, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:09.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't let Big Sister...{\i0}\NHow could you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:11.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mixing in that stuff was bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:12.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?{\i0}\NMixing in that stuff was bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:16.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to turn Belldandy\ninto a shameless little tramp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:17.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:20.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all your fault for butting in like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:24.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I know! The antidote...\nyou've got to start making an antidote!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take 30 hours to come up with one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:27.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That long?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:31.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The spell has a 24-hour effect,\nso it should wear off before...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I can cook up an antidote.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:38.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want you to take me\nshopping downtown today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:43.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, sure! I'm just going to\nwash up first, so wait for me, okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:44.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:47.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now what's gotten into her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:51.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy's seems so aggressive today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:55.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's because I've\nalways been too timid until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:59.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to wash your back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:02.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! I've already washed it,\nso you don't have to bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:07.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But Keiichi...are you saying you\ndon't want me to wash your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:10.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:11.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:16.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'm getting out now, so\ncould we do this another time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:21.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:25.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, asking you to take me\nshopping on such short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:29.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no problem. If you want to do\nsomething like that, it's no trouble at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:31.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:35.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi...you're so kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You...really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, my!{\i0}\NOw! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:47.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going on a date\nwith Keiichi today. Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:48.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Chu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:58.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Banpei?\NPull yourself together, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:01.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the rest of\nthe day's gonna be like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:07.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are walking around\nin familiar surroundings...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:10.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but for some reason,\nmy heart's pounding today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:13.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And just look how her eyes\nare glistening...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:16.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's trying to\nsend some kind of message?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:17.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:19.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:24.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um...do you think people\ncan tell we're a couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:25.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to be with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:29.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, no!{\i0}\NYou don't want to be with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:30.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:32.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:36.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's all right if we\nact like a couple, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:42.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is all right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:43.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Uh-huh!{\i0}\NThis is all right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:46.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:47.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:51.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! My Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:56.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard Belldandy\nsay anything like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:12:00.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now she's got me feeling\nreally self-conscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:06.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this, I bet\nyou'd look good in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:08.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:12.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of clothes\ndo you want to try on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:14.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What would I try on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:16.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If it were up to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:20.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:24.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How lovely! Which do you think\nwould look most becoming on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:31.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to put something like this on,\nand climb into bed with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:35.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, these aren't\nclothes, you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:37.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't look good in them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's not what I meant...{\i0}\nI wouldn't look good in them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:43.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell me which one you like best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:46.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, then...how about that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:50.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's charming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:55.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then.\nI'm going to go try it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:13:02.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe my Big Sister would\neven look at such a vulgar outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:05.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! This is no time\nfor you to browse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:07.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it's so adorable...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:10.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, you wouldn't\nknow anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:12.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:13.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing, actually...{\i0}\NWhat does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:16.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind! We've got\nto go after Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:31.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a heart attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:36.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If she walked around dressed like that\neveryday, I don't think I could take it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:39.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not that it would be such\na bad thing, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:41.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:45.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind giving me\na sip of that, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:48.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you have your own drink, Belldandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:51.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to try what\nyou're having, Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:53.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:54.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:56.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:06.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here. I enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:15.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to drink from this,\nwould that make it a secondhand kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:18.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?\NThere's still some left!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:21.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to drink it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:23.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Keiichi!\N{\i1}Bottoms up, Keiichi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:27.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy went to the trouble\nof planting her lips on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:30.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I might never get this\nkind of chance again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:33.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:35.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:42.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:52.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Coming to a place like this...\njust what are they up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:56.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, this is the first time we've\ncome to see a movie together, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:58.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:03.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting to come here,\nyou know...with you, Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:05.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:11.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's really going on here...why are\nyou acting like this today, Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:16.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand\nwhat goes on in a girl's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:22.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's the trailer for Winter Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:30.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no matter how we got to this\npoint, I am getting to see a movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:32.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...with Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:37.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Movie theaters are like a strange world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:40.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The onscreen images we see\nin the darkness are surreal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:45.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes it feels as if you're forced to\nbe aware of the opposite sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:48.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Especially on a day like today...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:53.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...how can I not be aware of her?\nI've got to calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:59.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:06.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want one too, Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:09.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:12.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Augh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:19.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...whoa! This is right\nout of a freakin' manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:22.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:24.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not that!{\i0}\NNo you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:35.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:38.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's something in my eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:40.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Would you take a look at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:41.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:46.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:50.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bizarre! Belldandy's behavior\nis definitely bizarre today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or it's some kind of huge mistake!\N{\i1}You have to get closer, or...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:53.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or it's some kind of huge mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:55.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or it's some kind of huge mistake!\N{\i1}...you won't be able to get it out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:56.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:59.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:02.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to get\nsomething out of her eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:05.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:09.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look at that.\NWhat do they think they're doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aren't they embarrassed?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:18.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You need to think about where you\nare before you throw those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:21.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you to tell me what to do?\NWhere's Big Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:28.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't have to run away like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:30.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't do that\nin front of other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:34.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home before\nsomething else freaky happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:37.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All righty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:39.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:41.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want to sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:50.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dreaming. I've got to be dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:01.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a lovely ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:03.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:10.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your back feels warm and inviting,\NKeiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:15.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,From where I'm sitting,\nI can feel your emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:19.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to go somewhere\nfar away, just you and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:22.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...with you, Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:37.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:39.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, it's getting late...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:45.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A little longer...is it all right if I have\nyou to myself a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:52.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:55.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, you're so kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:02.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The potion should be wearing off soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:06.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad they can't just go\nall the way first, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:13.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't just leave me behind\nlike this! Okay, you asked for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:24.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't spent time alone\nlike this lately, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:25.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:27.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.53,0:19:30.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, I have to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:31.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}B-B-B...Belldandy!{\i0}\NKeiichi, I have to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:32.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}B-B-B...Belldandy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:34.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}B-B-B...Belldandy!{\i0}\nI love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:38.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:40.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:48.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right...she's a goddess and I'm a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:51.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it wrong for me\nto get closer to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:55.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy will have to go\nback to Heaven some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:58.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When that day comes,\nwill I be able to let her go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:04.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved Keiichi...all I want is\nto stay with you a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:08.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right...I'm just making excuses\nbecause I'm spineless!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:11.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just like everyone says,\nI'm being a total wimp here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.84,0:20:15.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love with Belldandy.\NAnd she even says...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:17.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:19.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:20.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:22.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, one more push!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:24.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not if I can help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:25.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh, what the...{\i0}\NNot if I can help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:28.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let him have Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:31.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can take me?\NThen bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:38.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:42.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is inevitable, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:45.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For us to want each other...\nit's natural...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:47.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one here but us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.44,0:20:51.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay in this world of\nours forever...just you and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:52.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:55.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting in their way!\N{\i1}Big Sister!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:21:00.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anything else in\nthe world, as long as I have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.06,0:21:02.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:05.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do this! You're\nnot yourself right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:09.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why not?\nIs it because you don't love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:22.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:23.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:27.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're an honest person, you don't\nhave a distrustful bone in your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:29.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And you're so kind to everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:34.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the truth is, I want you to only\nbe kind to me...no, wait, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:35.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:41.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to say it, but\nI'm in love with the normal, genuine you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:48.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I love you more when\nyou're being yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:50.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:52.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I love you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:54.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:21:58.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:06.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so pissed! That's my Big Sister...\N{\i1}Good for you, Belldandy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:06.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so pissed! That's my Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.82,0:22:08.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so pissed! That's my Big Sister...\n{\i1}It's mostly thanks to my Seeds of Love...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:10.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's mostly thanks to my Seeds of Love...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.56,0:22:14.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And by the way, Skuld!\NYou know what to expect, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.66,0:22:19.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your punishment for touching\nmy stuff without my permission...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.27,0:22:24.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:26.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.37,0:22:29.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.40,0:22:31.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:34.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This device only goes around and\naround!\N{\i1}Don't show me those useless things!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.01,0:22:35.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't show me those useless things!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.68,0:22:38.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Deep down, those two are really close,\nhuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:42.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So horribly simplistic!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:52.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always believe in yourself and\nyour Dreams. You have a wing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.87,0:22:57.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always believe in yourself and\nyour Dreams. You have a wing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:23:02.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you so much it hurts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.64,0:23:08.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it hurts me that\nI can't tell you how I feel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:13.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You and I have matching hearts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.35,0:23:18.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So we must share the\nsame scars deep down inside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.49,0:23:23.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now that I'm in your arms,\nI think I can catch...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.93,0:23:28.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...your pounding heartbeat this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.89,0:23:34.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nobody else matters...\NAll we have to do is gaze at each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:39.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right for your heart to flutter...\NAll we have to do is love each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:44.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your heart, and\nride that favorable wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.81,0:23:50.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't run away from happiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.96,0:23:55.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll always be waiting for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:24:01.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So come rest your wings anytime.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.07,0:24:06.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right to cry...\nanytime you need to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.07,0:24:11.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just want to see you again...\NAll we have to do is love each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.71,0:24:16.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your heart, and\nride that favorable wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.68,0:24:22.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just want you to be happy.{\i0}
